</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="25.[156,771,1414,1467]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
<emphasis box="[156,281,1414,1435]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Etymology.</emphasis>
Latin diminutive noun for base, referring to the large setae at the base of the ovipositor.
</paragraph>
